@startuml Sequence_Notifications

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Notification API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "WebSocket" as WS

== Generate Notification ==
System -> API: Event occurs
API -> DB: Create notification
DB --> API: Notification created
API -> WS: Send real-time notification
WS --> Client: Push notification
Client --> User: Show notification badge

== View Notifications ==
User -> Client: Click notifications
Client -> API: GET /api/notifications
API -> DB: Get user notifications
DB --> API: Notifications list
API --> Client: Return notifications
Client --> User: Display notifications

== Mark as Read ==
User -> Client: Click notification
Client -> API: PUT /api/notifications/:id/read
API -> DB: Update notification status
DB --> API: Notification updated
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Update UI

== Delete Notification ==
User -> Client: Delete notification
Client -> API: DELETE /api/notifications/:id
API -> DB: Delete notification
DB --> API: Notification deleted
API --> Client: Success response
Client --> User: Remove from list

@enduml

